Package com.observability.modeling.probe.descriptor.entities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Collect
    The class defines the metrics which the user wants to collect from the list of available metrics.
    DbType  
    ElementTag
    The class creates an element tag and its related attributes.
    Machine
    The class defines the structure of a machine.
    The parameters required for a machine would be contained in this.
    Metric
    This class defines the semantic structure of a Metric.
    The metric identifier (tag) and metric name would go in name and the value parameter respectively.
    Obsolete_DescriptorElement
    Represents an element inside a descriptor file.
    Obsolete_PluginDefinition
    Parses the descriptors in a given directory and converts them to a manageable entity hierarchy.
    Parameter
    The abstract class defines the attributes and methods needed to define parameters for any type of annotation.
    Any new annotation would need to extend this class.
